title: The Anthony Cumia Show 2014-09-10 (MP4)
description:
Wednesday, September 10, 2014

A pajama clad Anthony starts the show talking about Jim Norton's appearance yesterday and the feedback that he has received from it. We hear that the President will be addressing ISIS tonight, talk about the skills that ISIS has on social media, and hear from a few callers. Ant tells us about a statement that Joe Rogan made on Jon Jones, we talk "click baiting," and watch and discuss a video from the kids of Ferguson. We then get into a video of Mike Tyson on Canadian TV, Keith tells us a sweet little cop story, and we tolerate additional listener calls. Ant wraps up with some entertainment news by updating us on Joan Rivers death and with a Justin Bieber news story.

**Not shot in HD today so no bitching about it**
